name: Lando System?
Lore: '''Lando''s not a system, he''s a man.'' Regardless of where Rebels flee, dark agents are sure to follow.',
Text: 'During your control phase, use 1 Force to move any one of your [Dagobah] icon characters of ability > 1 to any [Cloud City] icon location where you have presence. If moving to a Cloud City site, this movement is free and you do not need presence.',
